        "faq_item_MzenLh": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Canvas Information",
            "icon": "none",
            "answer": "<h5>🖼️ Canvas Print </h5><p>Our Canvas Prints are produced on 350g premium matte canvas with a rich, textured surface that brings the image to life. Hand-stretched over deep Nordic pine wood frames for a true gallery feel.</p><p>• No glass needed — no reflections, only pure art<br/>• Delivered fully assembled and ready to hang<br/>• Comes with a Certificate of Authenticity<br/>• Available sizes: 30×40 cm, 50×70 cm and 70×100 cm<br/>• Custom sizes available: <a>info@elleryart.com</a></p><p></p><p><strong><br/></strong> </p><h5>🖤 Canvas floating frame</h5><p>A minimal, modern frame designed to elevate the artwork.</p><p>• Creates a subtle shadow gap for a gallery-style finish<br/>• Hand-assembled for a flawless fit<br/>• Premium wood in black, white, oak or dark oak<br/>• Adds depth, dimension and a sophisticated final touch</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_VtWLbe": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "question": "Fine Art Information",
            "icon": "none",
            "answer": "<h5>🖨️ Fine Art Paper</h5><p>Our Fine Art Prints are produced with museum-quality pigment inks on 230g archival matte paper. The surface gives a soft, premium feel that captures every detail with depth and authenticity. Designed for long-lasting quality and made in Sweden.</p><p>• Limited edition - once sold out, it will never return<br/>• Produced on demand for a sustainable, exclusive experience<br/>• Comes with a Certificate of Authenticity<br/>• Available sizes: 30×40 cm, 50×70 cm and 70×100 cm<br/>• Custom sizes available: <a>info@elleryart.com</a></p><p></p><h4><strong><br/></strong>🪵 Frame for Fine Art</h4><p>Enhance your artwork with a handcrafted solid wood frame.<br/>Professionally mounted, ready to hang - straight from the box.</p><p>• Premium wood finishes: black, white, natural oak, dark oak<br/>• Crystal-clear glas for a glare-free viewing experience<br/>• Custom framed in Sweden with precision and care</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_da9JCQ": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Shipping Information",
            "icon": "none",
            "answer": "<p>All artworks are made on demand and produced specifically for your order.<br/><br/>🇸🇪 <strong>Sweden</strong><br/>Standard: 3–7 business days<br/>Priority: 1–5 business days</p><p>🇪🇺 <strong>EU</strong><br/>Standard: 3–9 business days<br/>Priority: 2–6 business days</p><p>🌍 <strong>Rest of World</strong><br/>Standard: 4–12 business days<br/>Priority: 3–8 business days<br/><br/>Tracking included. Public holidays excluded.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
